These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, russian, colombian, canadian, indonesian, indian, argentine
1. the russian is in the middle##1
2. the russian is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the malaysian is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the argentine is on the far left##1
6. the indian is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | argentine | canadian | indonesian | russian | colombian | malaysian | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, musician, designer, dressmaker, journalist, project-manager, social-worker
1. the social-worker is on the far right##1
2. the scientist is on the far left##1
3. the scientist is on the left of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left of the designer##1
5. the dressmaker is on the right of the project-manager##1
6. the social-worker is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | scientist | journalist | designer | project-manager | dressmaker | musician | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, gardening, photography, traveling, chess, magic-tricks, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | chess | singing | magic-tricks | photography | dancing | gardening | traveling |

 #################################

 
