.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-5::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, chinchilla, goat, cat, bird, rat
1. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla | goat | bird | hamster | pony | cat |

