.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, animation, musical, family, spy, martial-arts, romance
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | animation | documentary | martial-arts | family | romance | musical |

